## ✅ 2. Create api/login_api.py

```
api/login_api.py
```

Code:

```python
import requests

BASE_URL = "https://reqres.in/api"


def login(email, password):

    url = f"{BASE_URL}/login"

    payload = {
        "email": email,
        "password": password
    }

    headers = {
        "Content-Type": "application/json"
    }

    response = requests.post(
        url,
        json=payload,
        headers=headers
    )

    return response
```

Correct enterprise style.

